pageProduct.name: Slim Secrets Choc Love Bites Milk Chocolate & Almond 36g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Crush your goals and eat chocolate! Delicious milk chocolate blended with crushed almonds that's low carb, gluten free and contains protein so you can enjoy all the pleasure without the gain! 

Gluten free
Good source of protein
Low carb
No added sugar
Good source of fibre
Keto friendly
Vegetarian
No artificial colours or flavours
No preservatives
No GMO ingredients

Warnings

Contains Milk & Soy

Ingredients

Milk Chocolate (90%) [Cocoa Solids (Cocoa Butter, Cocoa Mass), Milk Protein Concentrate, Soluble Dietary Fibre (Polydextrose), Erythritol, Anhydrous Milk Fat, Natural Sweetener (Stevia), Natural Vanilla Flavour, Emulsifiers (476, 322 From Soy)], Crushed Roasted Almonds (10%)
